<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/416376-have-you-had-a-similar-experience-in">Have you had a similar experience in Paris? If yes or no, do you think this is an experience that is natural and common in maturing adults? Is there value in having an experience like the one in Giovanni&#39;s Room? Does such an experience need to end so negatively?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_416376'><a id="like_count_community_question_416376" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/416376?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F38462.Giovanni_s_Room">like</a></span>

